字节序转换
netinet/in.h:
    htonl,htons,ntohl,ntohs

socket地址
bits/socket.h:
    sockaddr
netinet/in.h:
    sockaddr_in

IP地址转换函数
arpa/inet.h:
    inet_addr,inet_aton,inet_ntoa

套接字socket
sys/types.h,sys/socket.h:
    socket,bind,listen,accept,connect,close

数据读写
sys/types.h,sys/socket.h:
    recv,send,recvfrom,sendto,recvmsg,sendmsg

socket选项,应在listen或connect之前设置
sys/socket.h:
    getsockopt,setsockopt

网络信息
netdb.h:
    gethostbyname,gethostbyaddr,getservbyname,getservbyport,getaddrinfo,getnameinfo